{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b156973c22","title":"“双百方针是多少人为民请愿的结果”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"51ed648685","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"b156973c22"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5deb6b92c9","name":"何玉辉"},{"id":"7d0a44a770","name":"王佐堂"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"cd6d1d2c70","name":"李燕吉"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6c0bf1ac5f","type":"title","text":"“双百方针是多少人为民请愿的结果”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"eebb78d2b0","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院李燕吉王佐堂何玉辉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"cd99ebb7ef","type":"paragraph","text":"李燕吉在党的「百花齐放百家争鸣」方针提出后说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"7e30a5b51d","type":"paragraph","text":"「不再提出来就不行了，瞧文艺界多方面的贫乏情形，这是多少人为民请愿的结果，如胡风就是。「百花齐放，百家争鸣」方针和胡风所提出的三十万言意见书有相同的地方……很钦佩胡风。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"24e6c1b792","type":"paragraph","text":"王佐堂说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"a279b7d219","type":"paragraph","text":"「百家争鸣是胡风提出的，毛主席是『歪打正着』。」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"11380dc501","type":"paragraph","text":"「共产党提出『长期共存互相监督』的方针，而实际各民主党派的存在是不平等的。既然提出这一方针，那么为什么民主党派不能发展呢？」「九三学社现在人家还不知道是高级社还是低级社呢？这证明党过去对民主党派是不重视的。」","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"3c2b05a480","type":"paragraph","text":"何玉辉说：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"edb3dc38bc","type":"paragraph","text":"「在国内，我把八大看作一个转折点，我想『百花齐放百家争鸣』看作一种标志，标志一切都通过争论来解决。过去说了些反话就当作落后，有时甚至于当成为反革命，现在是结束了。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"f7b1a73484","type":"paragraph","text":"「过去有好些人都把话别在心里未说出来，假如不解决，就迟早会发生匈牙利事件，后来毛主席说：无论如何要让人民说话时，我更是非常高兴了。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"5bb7531290","type":"paragraph","text":"何宜章说：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"022472f2a7","type":"paragraph","text":"「共产党和民主党派有矛盾，为何不取消它？」","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"cb2c00b5ec","type":"paragraph","text":"林墨荫说：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"d5587dde55","type":"paragraph","text":"「我院的民主党派为什么只是做视词，只做扩大会议成员，院报为什么不见他们的尖锐批评，这能说是互相监督吗？」","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"6c8a1ff6d5","type":"paragraph","text":"金荣新说：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"},{"id":"04975bc242","type":"paragraph","text":"「民主党派都是些老头，二十年后都死了，怎么会长期共存呢？」","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22"}],"page":{"id":"bcc69e132f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b156973c22","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}